name: Energy
description: This is the stuff that makes the world go round. Make sure you never run out, otherwise lights out!

name: Iron Ore
description: The raw form of the fundemental metal in an expansive space empire.

name: Limestone
description: Dead sea critters that have been squished and calcified into a delicious carbonate. Even then do they prove to be useful.

name: Concrete
description: Need a hard project done? Look no further than the crete of con. This substance is strong and sturdy but it cracks under pressure, just like my mental health.

name: Inversium
description: A spacetime anomly where this material contains negative mass, creating a gravitational repulsion.

name: Hydrogen
description: The most common yet crucial element in the universe.

name: Helium
description: A common noble gas that somehow escapes both mining and handling. Plus it can give some species silly voices! How cool is that?

name: Oxygen
description: An easily excited element who gets along with everyone- sometimes too well...
